data.title: 56th Stryker Brigade Combat Team - NTC 2018
data.meta_description: Soldiers of the 56th Stryker Brigade Combat Team, 28th Infantry Division, Pennsylvania Army National Guard completed their month-long annual training at the National Training Center, Fort Irwin, California July-August 2018. (U.S. Army National Guard photos by members of the 213th Regional Support Group and 56th Stryker Brigade Combat Team, 28th Infantry Division, Pennsylvania Army National Guard)
